    },
    "daicMode_behavior": "Auto-trigger logic MUST check CC_SESSION_MODE before firing WRITE-CAPABLE skills. If CC_SESSION_MODE is undefined/null, treat as DISCUSS (read-only). ANALYSIS-ONLY skills may run in any mode.",
